ing: 1 (16 ounce) package frozen stir-fry vegetables (sliced green, red, and yellow peppers and white onions)
n: Oh So Easy Sweet and Sour Meatballs
des: "This is by no means gourmet, but it was tasty and the kids loved it, even the veggies! It's great way to use frozen meatballs."
ins: Stir vegetables, meatballs, apricot jam, salad dressing, and soy sauce together in a skillet over medium heat. Cover the skillet and cook the mixture until the vegetables and meatballs are heated through completely, 15 to 20 minutes. Serve over rice.
